info:

paths:

            application/json:

          description: Bad Request
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                $ref: 'errors.yml#/components/schemas/ProblemResponse'

      description: Description of Ping
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 0
            maxLength: 20
          in: query
          name: responseWith
          description: response with this message
tags:

  - name: Base Route
